data.description: Pack your bags and move on in! Located in the beautiful city of Wyoming, this 3 bed and 2 bath home has so much to offer! Some amazing interior features include a roomy kitchen, foyer with coat closet, and a beautiful den with fireplace. Not to mention, the master has a large walk-in closet and there is main floor laundry. On the exterior you'll find a detached garage, fenced in back yard, and large driveway big enough for 3 cars. Not to mention, there is a full basement with plenty of storage and a sliding glass door on the main floor walking out to a nice sized back deck. Some updates include a newer furnace, hot water heater, GFI plugs, and some flooring throughout. Located close to Godfrey-Lee Schools and Pinery Park location is great! Call for your showing today!
